The package libpq provides CMake integration:

    find_package(PostgreSQL REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE PostgreSQL::PostgreSQL)

libpq provides pkg-config modules:

  # PostgreSQL libecpg library
  libecpg

  # PostgreSQL libecpg_compat library
  libecpg_compat

  # PostgreSQL libpgtypes library
  libpgtypes

  # PostgreSQL libpq library
  libpq
